Make Circle and Swiss Roll Datasets

Create Circle Dataset

We write a function that generate a 1-manifold circumference of a circle in 3 dimensions.

xy_tilt(X, flow, labels, xtilt=0, ytilt=0)

{% endraw %} {% raw %}
{% endraw %} {% raw %}

{% endraw %} {% raw %}
{% endraw %} {% raw %}

{% endraw %} {% raw %}
